<H2><U><img align=top src="vinelarge.jpg"><a name="language"><font size=6>Haida Language Resources</a></font></u></H2>


<H2>
Our Online Haida Language Materials</H2>


<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.native-languages.org/haida_words.htm
">Haida Vocabulary</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Our list of vocabulary words in the Haida language, with comparison to words in Athabaskan languages.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.native-languages.org/haida_animals.htm
">Haida Animal Words</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Picture dictionary of animal words in the Haida language.
<BR>

<h2>
<A name="materials">Haida</a> Dictionaries, Audio Tapes and Language Resources
</u><BR><font size=2>Our organization earns a commission from any book bought through these links</font>
</h2>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1555000878/natilangofthe-20
">Haida Dictionary</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Thorough dictionary of the Haida language for sale, covering the Skidegate, Masset, and Alaskan dialects.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0660196166/natilangofthe-20
">Gaaw Xaadee Gyaahlaangaay</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Audio CD set of Haida speakers telling traditional stories in Haida and English.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0803218222/natilangofthe-20
">Haida Syntax</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Linguistics texts on the grammar and structure of the Haida language.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"><b><A HREF="
http://www.native-languages.org/dictionary.htm
">Native American Language Dictionaries</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Haida and other American Indian dictionaries and language materials for sale.
<BR>

